    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, you and your @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.hWygu85vBW9MqyHm]{Animal Companion} can share in each others' pains.</p><p>Whenever you are hit by an attacker you can see and your animal companion is within 60 feet of you, you can use your reaction to gain resistance to all damage taken that turn. The damage take is split evenly between you and your animal companion.</p><p>Your animal companion can also use its reaction to perform the same damage reduction when it's hit by an attacker it can see and is within 60 feet of you. The damage it takes that turn is split evenly between you.</p>",
